**From `@chakra-ui/react` (native Chakra):**

```tsx
import {
  Alert, Avatar, Badge, Box, Button, Card, Container, Field,
  Flex, Heading, HStack, Icon, Input, Link, NativeSelect,
  Separator, Spacer, Spinner, Stack, Table, Tabs, Text,
  Textarea, VStack, useDisclosure
